@startuml
title ETR Study API — Business flow (analyst view)

autonumber
hide footbox

actor    "Learner"       as Learner
boundary "Client app\n(web / mobile)" as ClientApp
control  "Study API"     as Api

== Authoring a new note (one-off) ==

Learner  -> ClientApp: writes a note\n(title, cue sheet, dense paragraph, bullets)
ClientApp -> Api: POST /api/v1/conspectuses
Api --> ClientApp: note accepted, first review\nscheduled ~1 hour later
ClientApp --> Learner: "Note saved"

== Daily study loop ==

Learner  -> ClientApp: opens the app
ClientApp -> Api: GET /api/v1/schedule/summary
Api --> ClientApp: workload counts per slot,\ndue now, due in the next 24h
ClientApp --> Learner: shows the load badge

Learner  -> ClientApp: starts a session
alt evening batch (curated)
  ClientApp -> Api: GET /api/v1/schedule/preview\n(window, deterministic seed)
  Api --> ClientApp: compact shuffled list
else full due queue
  ClientApp -> Api: GET /api/v1/conspectuses/due
  Api --> ClientApp: up to 100 due notes, oldest first
end

loop for each note in the batch
  Learner  -> ClientApp: taps a card
  ClientApp -> Api: GET /api/v1/conspectuses/{id}
  Api --> ClientApp: full note (cue sheet + dense paragraph + bullets)
  ClientApp --> Learner: renders the card
  Learner  -> ClientApp: recalls the material,\npicks a verdict

  alt recalled effortlessly
    ClientApp -> Api: POST /conspectuses/{id}/actions/review\ntag = easy
    Api --> ClientApp: next review pushed further out\n(slot advances)
  else remembered with effort
    ClientApp -> Api: POST /conspectuses/{id}/actions/review\ntag = hard
    Api --> ClientApp: next review sooner\n(step back one slot)
  else forgot
    ClientApp -> Api: POST /conspectuses/{id}/actions/review\ntag = forgot
    Api --> ClientApp: back to the front of the queue\n(slot = A)
  end

  opt learner noticed a specific mistake
    Learner  -> ClientApp: writes a short note about the mistake
    ClientApp -> Api: POST /api/v1/errors\n(optionally linked to this card)
    Api --> ClientApp: mistake recorded
  end
end

== Occasional stewardship ==

Learner  -> ClientApp: edits an old note

ClientApp -> Api: PATCH /api/v1/conspectuses/{id}
Api --> ClientApp: note updated (review schedule untouched)

Learner  -> ClientApp: opens the note's history
ClientApp -> Api: GET /api/v1/conspectuses/{id}/history
Api --> ClientApp: past reviews + edits, oldest first

Learner  -> ClientApp: archives the note
ClientApp -> Api: DELETE /api/v1/conspectuses/{id}
Api --> ClientApp: note archived, related mistakes\nkept but unlinked

@enduml
